{"tid":1463781,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"轉貼 藍色身份證","createTime":"2019-08-13T13:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-16T02:12:19.000Z","uid":6345,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8c58280fe734ffc875d27db8f8106c1012ed3be9","tid":1463781,"uid":6345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:45:50.000Z","msg":"轉貼<br />\n<br />\n尋晚同老闆食飯，同枱有位老人家同酒樓經理吹水，傾完一輪，經理明顯係撐政府，但老人還未表態，然後經理問老人：「依家學生搞到咁亂點解決好？」<br />\n<br />\n老人淡定說：「送中法無問題，想送中就拎藍色身份証，唔想就拎黃色，第時犯罪藍色就返大陸審，黃色就係香港審，睇下邊個願意返上去囉。」 <br />\n最後老人就笑問經理你想拎咩色身份証呀？經理一面尷尬向大家笑一笑，連回答的勇氣都沒有就行開了。 <br />\n<br />\n現實就是好多呢類人，盲撐政府，自己唔想送中，但又鬧學生搞事？!<br />\n<br />\n比身邊藍絲選擇下"},{"pid":"1a836a8345a07fa6e91f06d9e9429c852c3b2373","tid":1463781,"uid":279253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:46:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ab025baa68bbbb78656f63cdc2e062ea8886623","tid":1463781,"uid":128600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"543f12cfb71f8c1aed0007c78da3d03f3ea7858c","tid":1463781,"uid":74182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:50:44.000Z","msg":"幾好saved"},{"pid":"c75ccb3cd9bf01b5c6ab4f396d3ea271a5d59b48","tid":1463781,"uid":88817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T13:53:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3980b1af2123ee3b31ef7ad43982907574ac6349","tid":1463781,"uid":77033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T00:02:14.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"1e65240e3e4856ab7cf810439835e9872de60cfe","tid":1463781,"uid":49138,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-16T02:10:41.000Z","msg":"智慧老人<br />\n如果哩家仲有人講&q